3. Stay active: Incorporate physical activity into your daily routine to improve cardiovascular endurance, muscle strength, and flexibility. Schedule regular workouts or engage in light exercise, such as walking, swimming, or yoga, to keep your body moving and prevent muscle atrophy. 
